presets.name: Alt Art Rock Space
presets.summary: Atmospheric and textural tone with layered modulation and spacey delays. Suited for experimental chords and dynamic lead lines.

presets.name: Alt Rock Big Muff Wall
presets.summary: Massive fuzz-laden tone with creamy sustain and thick low-end. Ideal for heavy riffs, layered overdubs, and shoegaze-like walls of sound.
